Description: Nice Clean 2012 Squier Classic Vibe Custom Telecaster in 3 tone sunburst finish and in excellent condition. The frets are shiny and super smooth with a nice dark rosewood fretboard. It comes with a a nice Fender Tweed Style Strap and Brand New Road Runner Hard Shell case. These cases ares super light weight and they are built to last as well as fitting the guitar nice and snug with a built in velcro neck strap to keep the guitar from moving around in the case.  Everything on the guitar works as it should with no scratchy or noisy pots and a nice smooth truss rod. It plays and feels really nice with classic tele tone.
